        ADDING NEW MUSICFILES
        Parameters:
        _title -
        _album -
        _interpret - //* @param _file Allows the user to add music-files from a local storage to the database The user can add an files with a prior allowed set of extension. and has to add a title and interpret and album of the audio-file. Title, interpret and album could later be used for sorting purposes. At the moment there are no character restrictions for the input of the title, interpret and album because its planned to outsource these to the forms of the web- or userinterface of the final program
